title: ERROR_FILE_SHARE_RESOURCE_CONFLICT

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_EVICT_INVALID_REQUEST
msg: Eviction of this node is invalid at this time. Due to quorum requirements node eviction will result in cluster shutdown. If it is the last node in the cluster, destroy cluster command should be used.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_SINGLETON_RESOURCE
msg: Only one instance of this resource type is allowed in the cluster.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_GROUP_SINGLETON_RESOURCE
msg: Only one instance of this resource type is allowed per resource group.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_RESOURCE_PROVIDER_FAILED
msg: The resource failed to come online due to the failure of one or more provider resources.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_RESOURCE_CONFIGURATION_ERROR
msg: The resource has indicated that it cannot come online on any node.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_GROUP_BUSY
msg: The current operation cannot be performed on this group at this time.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_NOT_SHARED_VOLUME
msg: The directory or file is not located on a cluster shared volume.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_INVALID_SECURITY_DESCRIPTOR
msg: The Security Descriptor does not meet the requirements for a cluster.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_SHARED_VOLUMES_IN_USE
msg: There is one or more shared volumes resources configured in the cluster. Those resources must be moved to available storage in order for operation to succeed.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_USE_SHARED_VOLUMES_API
msg: This group or resource cannot be directly manipulated. Use shared volume APIs to perform desired operation.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_BACKUP_IN_PROGRESS
msg: Back up is in progress. Please wait for backup completion before trying this operation again.

title: ERROR_NON_CSV_PATH
msg: The path does not belong to a cluster shared volume.

title: ERROR_CSV_VOLUME_NOT_LOCAL
msg: The cluster shared volume is not locally mounted on this node.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_WATCHDOG_TERMINATING
msg: The cluster watchdog is terminating.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_RESOURCE_VETOED_MOVE_INCOMPATIBLE_NODES
msg: A resource vetoed a move between two nodes because they are incompatible.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_INVALID_NODE_WEIGHT
msg: The request is invalid either because node weight cannot be changed while the cluster is in disk-only quorum mode, or because changing the node weight would violate the minimum cluster quorum requirements.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_RESOURCE_VETOED_CALL
msg: The resource vetoed the call.

title: ERROR_RESMON_SYSTEM_RESOURCES_LACKING
msg: Resource could not start or run because it could not reserve sufficient system resources.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_RESOURCE_VETOED_MOVE_NOT_ENOUGH_RESOURCES_ON_DESTINATION
msg: A resource vetoed a move between two nodes because the destination currently does not have enough resources to complete the operation.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_RESOURCE_VETOED_MOVE_NOT_ENOUGH_RESOURCES_ON_SOURCE
msg: A resource vetoed a move between two nodes because the source currently does not have enough resources to complete the operation.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_GROUP_QUEUED
msg: The requested operation can not be completed because the group is queued for an operation.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_RESOURCE_LOCKED_STATUS
msg: The requested operation can not be completed because a resource has locked status.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_SHARED_VOLUME_FAILOVER_NOT_ALLOWED
msg: The resource cannot move to another node because a cluster shared volume vetoed the operation.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_NODE_DRAIN_IN_PROGRESS
msg:
A node drain is already in progress.

This value was also named

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_DISK_NOT_CONNECTED
msg: Clustered storage is not connected to the node.

title: ERROR_DISK_NOT_CSV_CAPABLE
msg: The disk is not configured in a way to be used with CSV. CSV disks must have at least one partition that is formatted with NTFS.

title: ERROR_RESOURCE_NOT_IN_AVAILABLE_STORAGE
msg: The resource must be part of the Available Storage group to complete this action.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_SHARED_VOLUME_REDIRECTED
msg: CSVFS failed operation as volume is in redirected mode.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_SHARED_VOLUME_NOT_REDIRECTED
msg: CSVFS failed operation as volume is not in redirected mode.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_CANNOT_RETURN_PROPERTIES
msg: Cluster properties cannot be returned at this time.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_RESOURCE_CONTAINS_UNSUPPORTED_DIFF_AREA_FOR_SHARED_VOLUMES
msg: The clustered disk resource contains software snapshot diff area that are not supported for Cluster Shared Volumes.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_RESOURCE_IS_IN_MAINTENANCE_MODE
msg: The operation cannot be completed because the resource is in maintenance mode.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_AFFINITY_CONFLICT
msg: The operation cannot be completed because of cluster affinity conflicts.

title: ERROR_CLUSTER_RESOURCE_IS_REPLICA_VIRTUAL_MACHINE
msg: The operation cannot be completed because the resource is a replica virtual machine.
